// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// DELIBERATELY EXCLUDED - nine packages, none of which has a consumer anywhere in
// RDCToolsLib, DUF or DFRefactor. Keeping the reasons visible matters: every one
// of these was invisible until the library was compiled on its own.
//
// (a) Name collisions - two packages declaring the same class:
//
//   cRDSlideOffOn.pkg               These two and cRDCSliderOffOn.pkg (included
//   cRDCSlideOffOn.pkg              above) ALL declare "Class cRDCSliderOffOn is a
//                                   cCommandLinkButton". Using more than one is a
//                                   duplicate-class error. The two excluded names
//                                   look like typo'd copies; none of the three has
//                                   a consumer, so the canonical one is a guess -
//                                   cRDCSliderOffOn.pkg, whose filename matches the
//                                   class it declares.
//
//   cRDCSkinComboBoxCJMenuItem.pkg  Declares the same "Class cSkinComboBoxCJMenuItem"
//                                   as cSkinComboBoxCJMenuItem.pkg. The latter is the
//                                   live one (DUFTestProgram.src Uses it).
//
// (b) Reference files that no longer exist - these fail with 4313:
//
//   cRDCIconView.pkg                Uses cIconPanel.pkg, which is in neither this
//                                   library nor the DataFlex Pkg folder. Note the
//                                   library does have cRDCIconPanel.pkg - this looks
//                                   like a name left behind by a rename.
//
//   cRDCDbRichEditor.pkg            Uses oRichEditFind.dg and oRichEditFindReplace.dg.
//                                   Neither exists here or in the DataFlex Pkg folder.
//
//   cRDCCJChangeColorMenuItem.pkg   The whole file is commented out under the header
//                                   "Obsolete code:" - it declares nothing at all. Its
//                                   base, cCJRTFMenuItem.pkg, is gone from DataFlex.
//
// (c) Needs software that is not part of a base DataFlex install:
//
//   cRDCCrystalDbAutoConnect.pkg    "Class cCrystalDbAutoConnect is a cCrystal" - needs
//                                   the Crystal Reports package.
//
// (d) Superseded:
//
//   RDCStatpnl.pkg                  Superseded by RDCStatusPanel.pkg.
//
// Every package in this list is a deletion candidate. Deleting the dead ones is a
// better answer than this comment; group (b) in particular is broken, not merely
// unused, and cannot be fixed without files nobody appears to still have.
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------


Send Info_Box "RDCToolsLib compiled clean." "Library smoke test"
